snippet.title: TAG: The Power of Paint | DigiPen Institute of Technology
snippet.description:
http://www.DigiPen.edu | DigiPen Institute of Technology

Tag is a first-person puzzle game that lets you alter the properties of any surface through the power of paint. Throw down various combinations of colored paints that help you rush, bounce, and climb your way through the city.

Download the game for free at:
https://www.digipen.edu/?id=1170&proj=1506

DigiPen Institute of Technology offers bachelor's and master's degree programs in computer science, computer engineering, game design, digital art and animation, and music and sound design.
